Package parser

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StandingsParser
    Interface for different categories of parsers that allows running.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CbsSportsParser
    Allows pulling of statistics data from tables in an html document, or indirectly from a url that is used to generate an html document, and divides this data into a list of data labels (headers), a list of lists of the statistics data, and a list of links to images related to individual teams.
    MLBParser
    Runs the parser for MLB data and prints verification output to console.
    NBAParser
    Runs the parser for NBA data and prints verification output to console.
    NFLParser
    Runs the parser for NFL data and prints verification output to console.
    ParserFactory
    Facilitates creation of parsers for each category of team data.
    ParserJUnit
    Tests valid and invalid (when applicable) implementations of CbsSportsParser methods.
    ScrapedData
    Creates an object that holds all of the scraped data consisting of team statistics, including the list of data labels (headers), lists of lists of statistics data, and list of associated team images.
    ScrapedDataJUnit
    Tests valid and invalid (when applicable) implementations of ScrapeData methods.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ParserEnum
    Enumerates parsers for each category of team data.
